halted fighting in the 8year war between iran and iraq the absence 
of any recent mining and achievements of european and us 
minesweepers in removing mines from international waters hamilton 
said tuesday night 
a fourship task force of hightechnology british hunt class 
minehunters arrived in the gulf in september 1987 following 
iranian mining of the area since then the royal navy has located 
and destroyed 10 mines 
hamilton said that should circumstances change britain would 
return three minehunters to the gulf 
