have anticipated 
the former radio announcer movie actor and afterdinner speaker 
came to the white house with more televisionrelated experience than 
any of his predecessors his 1964 television speech for barry 
goldwater helped catapult reagan into two terms as governor of 
california where he continued to sharpen his television skills as 
well as gaining experience in government 
in his first major televised speech from the oval office he 
outlined his tax reduction program on july 27 1981 using charts 
and a pointer to make his case that the administration plan was more 
fair than that proposed by democrats in congress he ended as he 
would so often thank you god bless you and good night 
but his statement from the oval office on nov 13 1986 that the 
arms sent to iran could easily fit into a single cargo plane and 
did not constitute a swap of arms for hostages failed to go over in 
congress reagan later had to admit mistakes had been made 
