where there is one country that has nuclear weapons and that country 
that has mass destruction weapons is not a signatory to the 
nonproliferation treaty and has refused to reach peace that 
nation constitutes a real threat to the peace and security of the 
region 
both the superpowers have thousands of tons of chemical weapons 
in storage and the united states has a program to develop new 
sophisticated systems 
another 20 nations including many at the conference possess the 
weapons or are in the process of developing them 
