problem said sussman 
jail has taught me fear fear of ever having to return zolp 
told lechner i stand here shamed today i stand here disgraced i 
am financially insolvent however i am rehabilitated he said 
but lechner harshly rejected zolps claim of acting out of 
character 
your conduct has been your character the judge said you 
are a con man 
